%20by%20wind-ruffled%20fur.%20From%20126%20identified%20individuals%2C%20the%20team%20used%20spatial%20capture-recapture%20models%20to%20estimate%20a%20total%20population%20of%20477%20snow%20leopards%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ladakh%20is%20home%20to%20an%20estimated%20477%20snow%20leopards%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Bubo%20Birding%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T154538.437_11zon-1751624156-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-462647%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELadakh%20is%20home%20to%20an%20estimated%20477%20snow%20leopards%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Bubo%20Birding%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20vision%20for%20coexistence%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20these%20figures%20are%20impressive%2C%20the%20real%20success%20lies%20in%20what%20is%20happening%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20centre%20of%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20conservation%20effort%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345716%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-india-trust-tsewang-namgail-himalayan-homestays-ladakh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESnow%20Leopard%20Conservancy%20India%20Trust%20(SLC-IT)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20initiative%20founded%20in%202003%20by%20mountaineer%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk%20and%20biologist%20Rodney%20Jackson.%20In%202013%2C%20after%20Wangchuk%E2%80%99s%20passing%2C%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%20returned%20from%20the%20United%20States%2C%20where%20he%20had%20been%20working%20as%20a%20wildlife%20biologist%2C%20to%20take%20over%20as%20director.%20His%20mission%20was%20to%20continue%20the%20work%20of%20building%20harmony%20between%20people%20and%20predators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20conservancy%E2%80%99s%20most%20important%20initiatives%20is%20a%20livestock%20insurance%20scheme%20designed%20to%20reduce%20human-wildlife%20conflict%2C%20a%20common%20issue%20in%20pastoral%20communities.%20Each%20household%20contributes%20Rs%20400%20per%20year%20to%20a%20village%20fund.%20If%20a%20snow%20leopard%20kills%20livestock%2C%20the%20family%20is%20compensated%2C%20they%20receive%20Rs%205%2C000%20for%20a%20small%20animal%20and%20Rs%207%2C000%20for%20a%20larger%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiving%20alongside%20the%20ferocious%20predator%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20dream%20for%20the%20pastoral%20communities%20of%20Ladakh.%20But%20maintaining%20their%20livelihoods%20through%20schemes%20like%20this%20makes%20it%20possible.%20Namgail%20says%20the%20felines%20are%20fondly%20called%20%E2%80%98Ri%20Gyancha%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98ornaments%20of%20the%20mountains%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETourism%