more%20time%20to%20do%20what%20he%20loves%3A%20engage%20with%20the%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I'm%20a%20bit%20sad%2C%20I%20go%20to%20my%20sister's%20or%20arrange%20to%20see%20my%20friends%3A%20they%20know%20how%20to%20make%20me%20laugh.%20My%20husband%20has%20made%20some%20friends%20through%20football.%20And%20the%20kids%20are%20not%20asking%20when%20they'll%20be%20going%20back%20to%20the%20UK%20as%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20like%20their%20school%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20have%20a%20swimming%20pool%20in%20the%20building.%20They%20enjoy%20hanging%20out%20with%20my%20siblings%20and%20their%20little%20cousin%20and%20having%20lunch%20with%20their%20grandma%20once%20a%20week.%20And%20they%20speak%20Spanish%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20I%20loved%20their%20British%20accents%2C%20I%20hated%20that%20they%20couldn't%20roll%20the%20%26quot%3Br%26quot%3B%20or%20say%20anything%20in%20Spanish%20apart%20from%20%26quot%3BHola%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Bc%C3%B3mo%20est%C3%A1s%26quot%3B.%20Now%20they%20can%20communicate%2C%20for%20real%2C%20and%20that's%20truly%20awesome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20still%20don't%20know%20how%20long%20we'll%20be%20staying%20here%2C%20but%20we%20know%20it%20was%20right%20to%20come%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20suffering.%20We%20may%20not%20have%20a%20fixed%20income%2C%20but%20we%20have%20a%20feeling%20that%20no%20one%20can%20take%20away%20from%20us.%20We%20feel%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsold-everything-moved-argentina-2-sons-been-worth-it-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751630161000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68669b5ff748d8c055f4ed4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsold-everything-moved-argentina-2-sons-been-worth-it-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Macarena%20Alvarez%20wanted%20her%20sons%20to%20experience%20both%20parents'%