th%20what%20it%20dubbed%20%26quot%3Bthe%20greatest%20hoodie%20ever%20made.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20company%20celebrated%20Independence%20Day%20with%20a%20version%20of%20the%20iconic%20American%20flag%20T-shirt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-made-in-usa-american-brands-domestic-manufacturing-benefits-challenges-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emade%20entirely%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Bayard%20said%20it%20was%20a%20challenge%20to%20achieve%20the%20kinds%20of%20production%20efficiencies%20that%20can%20lower%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20factories%20can%20produce%20high-quality%20clothing%2C%20but%20it%20often%20comes%20at%20a%20premium%20price.%20For%20example%2C%20American%20Giant's%20website%20lists%20this%20year's%20US%20flag%20tee%20for%20%2465.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBayard%20said%20the%20reasons%20for%20this%20include%20finer%20yarns%20and%20a%20more%20labor-intensive%20sewing%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20products%20are%20premium%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20optimized%20for%20top%2C%20top%20quality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20Walmart%20approached%20him%20with%20a%20challenge%20to%20produce%20a%20made-in-US%20T-shirt%20at%20the%20retail%20giant's%20famously%20low%20prices.%20This%20was%20part%20of%20what%20is%20now%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.walmart.com%2Fsuppliers%2Finvesting-in-american-jobs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24350%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20commitment%20to%20invest%20in%20sourcing%20products%20that%20support%20American%20jobs%20until%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22433%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20American%20flag%20t-shirt%20made%20by%20American%20Giant%20sold%20at%20Walmart.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6866ba9c85e81483682d5adf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22325%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmerican%20Giant%20sells%20a%20version%20of%20its%20American%20flag%20T-shirt%20at%20Walmart.%3Cp%3EWalmart%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Bayard%20thought%20that%20the%20lowest%20possible%20price%20for%20an%20American-made%20shirt%20would%20have%20been%20%2420%20and%20that%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bincredibly%20difficult%26quot%3B%20to%20make.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20were%20able%20to%20make%20a%20shirt%20that%20is%20now%20available%20online%20and%20across%20roughly%201%2C500%20Walmart%20stores%20for%20%2412.98%20%E2%80%94%20one-fifth%20of%20the%20price%20of%20the%20top-of-the-line%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20Giant%20developed%20a%20design%20that%20lowered%20costs%20by%20using%20a%20slightly%20thicker%20yarn%20and%20a%20tubular-knit%20pattern%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20side-sewn%20style%20of%20his%20main%20shirts%2C%20Bayard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20vastly%20more%20important%20part%20of%20the%20costing%20is%20when%20you%20have%20Walmart%20and%20the%20volumes%20that%20they%20put%20there%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20huge%20%E2%80%94%20and%20staying%20committed%20to%20the%20program%20for%20an%20extended%20period%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBayard%20stands%20firmly%20behind%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20less%20expensive%20Walmart%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20we're%20putting%20great%20quality%20stuff%20into%20the%20market%2C%20and%20we're%20offering%20these%20different%20entry%20points%20for%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBayard%20said%20the%20first%20design%20for%20Walmart%2C%20released%20last%20year%2C%20exceeded%20sales%20expectations%20and%20was%20expanded%20to%20include%20four%20styles%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20episode%20highlights%20one%20of%20the%20major%20hurdles%20to%20bringing%20back%20US%20manufacturing%20more%20broadly.%20The%20costs%20of%20starting%20(or%20restarting)%20industrial%20production%20can%20be