%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edelivery%20driver%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20driven%20around%20the%20US%20while%20doing%20gig%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETorres%20has%20visited%20all%2050%20US%20states%20while%20working%20for%20apps%20like%20Lyft%20and%20DoorDash.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Kreskin%20Torres%2C%20a%20gig%20worker%20who%20has%20visited%20each%20of%20the%2050%20US%20states%20while%20working%20as%20a%20ride-hailing%20driver%20for%20Lyft.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interview%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-forward-dispatch-trips-riders-drivers-study-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erideshare%20driver%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Lyft%20for%20about%20nine%20years%20now.%20I%20started%20out%20in%20Baltimore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20year%20in%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrocery-shopping-differences-american-in-london-uk-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evisited%20London%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20month.%20I%20realized%20on%20that%20trip%20that%20travel%20gives%20you%20ideas%20and%20inspires%20you%20to%20try%20new%20things.%20When%20I%20came%20back%2C%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20I%20want%20to%20see%20my%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20a%20flexible%20job%20where%20I%20could%20meet%20different%20people%20and%20plan%20my%20own%20schedule.%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20minimize%20what%20I%20owned%20and%20focus%20on%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20road%20trip%20I%20took%20was%20from%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaltimore-basic-income-parents-afford-housing-get-jobs-ubi-gbi-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBaltimore%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20the%20West%20Coast.%20I%20left%20in%20February%202018.%20I've%20been%20traveling%20and%20doing%20gig%20work%20full-time%20since%20then.%20Most%20months%2C%20I%20make%20between%20%242%2C500%20and%20%243%2C000%20in%20gross%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20to%20all%2050%20states%2C%20and%20some%20of%20them%20I've%20visited%20three%20or%20four%20times.%20That%20took%20about%20three%20years%20to%20do.%20I%20was%20stuck%20at%2049%20for%20a%20while%20because%20of%20the%20pandemic.%20When%20I%20hit%20my%2050th%20state%20%E2%80%94%20Hawaii%20%E2%80%94%20I%20ended%20up%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kitv.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Fthe-rideshare-foodie-comes-to-honolulu%2Farticle_aca63570-d4a8-11ec-a9d7-5f8545fd2628.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocal%20news%3C%2Fa%3E%20talking%20about%20my%20travels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20pick%20a%20new%20home%20base%20every%20few%20months%20and%20visit%20towns%20nearby%20to%20do%20rideshare%20and%20delivery%20work.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Pittsburgh%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20in%20West%20Virginia%20for%20a%20while.%20I%20also%20want%20to%20be%20in%20Latrobe%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20later%20this%20summer.%20They%20claim%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbananasplitfest.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebanana%20split%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20invented%20there%2C%20and%20they%20have%20a%20festival%20for%20it%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20get%20into%20a%20new%20town%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20I%20normally%20do%20is%20stop%20at%20Planet%20Fitness%2C%20where%20I%20stretch%20and%20shower%20after%20a%20long%20drive.%20From%20there%2C%20I%20usually%20head%20to%20an%20Airbnb%20for%20a%20few%20days%20to%20relax.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20sleep%20in%20my%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERidesharing%20is%20my%20main%20work.%20There%20have%20been%20some%20places%20where%20I%20couldn't%20drive%20for%20Lyft%20because%20local%20laws%20require%20drivers%20to%20have%20local%20licenses.%20In%20those%20places%2C%20I%20delivered%20through%20DoorDash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDriving%20around%20the%20US%20has%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20make%20money%20in%20different%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%2C%20I%20lived%20and%20worked%20in%20Phoenix%20for%20a%20year%2C%20but%20I%20realized%20that%20I%20could%20make%20more%20money%20in%20Tucson.%20It's%20not%20as%20spread%20out%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20college%20town%2C%20so%20you%20tend%20to%20get%20more%20high-paying%2C%20short-distance%20trips.%20If%20you%20go%20there%20in%20the%20winter%2C%20there's%20even%20more%20demand%20from%20people%20who%20come%20for%20the%20warmer%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20parts%20of%20the%20US%20are%20less%20competitive%20than%20others.%20Many%20big%20cities%20are%20oversaturated%20with%20drivers.%20In%20places%20like%20Chicago%2C%20you'll%20see%20hundreds%20of%20them%20waiting%20at%20the%20airport%20to%20claim%20a%20ride.%20In%20Tucson%2C%20you%20may%20see%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d8ba063-6206-46bf-8b12-7a03e1d7246e%5C%22%3EGig%20work%20helped%20me%20pursue%20my%20interest%20in%20food%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20started%20traveling%2C%20it%20struck%20me%20how%20certain%20regions%20of%20the%20US%20are%20known%20for%20different%20foods.%20I%20started%20paying%20attention%20to%20which%20crops%20were%20growing%20around%20me%20and%20what%20the%20places%20I%20visited%20were%20known%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20trying%20regional%20foods%20part%20of%20my%20travels.%20I%20created%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ridesharefoodies.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20Rideshare%20Foodie.%20I%20post%20photos%20of%20local%20cuisines%2C%20such%20as%20pickles%20brined%20in%20Kool-Aid%20from%20Mississippi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFood%20is%20also%20a%20great%20conversation%20topic%20with%20the%20people%20I%20drive%20for%20Lyft.%20They%20recommend%20places%20to%20eat%20or%20foods%20to%20try.%20Sometimes%2C%20it's%20a%20restaurant%2C%20and%20other%20times%2C%20it's%20home%20cooking%20at%20a%20barbecue%20or%20a%20block%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I've%20stayed%20somewhere%20long%20enough%2C%20I%20can%20also%20make%20recommendations.%20When%20I%20was%20in%20Rapid%20City%2C%20South%20Dakota%2C%20I%20picked%20up%20a%20lady%20from%20the%20airport%20who%20was%20from%20Brooklyn%2C%20New%20York.%20She%20asked%20where%20she%20could%20find%20some%20great%20Italian%20food.%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMa'am%2C%20they're%20not%20known%20for%20their%20Italian%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20she%20should%20try%20the%20beef%20instead.%20That%20area%20is%20known%20for%20cattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20I've%20learned%20in%20my%20work%20is%20that%20many%20people%20rarely%20travel%20beyond%20their%20town%20or%20even%20their%20neighborhood.%20And%20when%20they%20do%20travel%2C%20they%20sometimes%20eat%20the%20same%20things%20as%20they%20do%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20lifestyle%20lets%20me%20try%20new%20things%20and%20meet%20lots%20of%20new%20people.%20The%20more%20that%20I%20travel%2C%20the%20more%20that%20I%20learn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20gig%20work%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20808-854-4501.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flyft-doordash-worker-describes-seeing-50-states-gig-work-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751622961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ebb3bf748d8c055f484c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flyft-doordash-worker-describes-seeing-50-states-gig-work-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kreskin%20Torres%2C%20who%20calls%20himself%20the%20Rideshare%20Foodie%2C%20has%20visited%20every%20US%20state%20while%20working%20for%20Lyft%20and%20DoorDash