his%20summertime%20dish.%20The%20salty%2C%20briny%20mix-ins%20give%20the%20salad%20a%20distinctly%20Mediterranean%20taste%20that%20felt%20a%20little%20unusual%2C%20but%20I%20preferred%20it%20to%20the%20typical%20mayonnaise-dressed%20pasta%20salad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20noodles%20and%20mix-ins%20are%20tossed%20in%20a%20dressing%20made%20with%20more%20sun-dried%20tomatoes%2C%20red%20wine%20vinegar%2C%20olive%20oil%2C%20capers%2C%20and%20garlic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20also%20need%20some%20freshly%20grated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-parmesan-cheese-good-for-you-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EParmesan%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20parsley%20to%20top%20the%20salad%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20preparation%20is%20quick%20and%20easy.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221248%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chopped%20vegetables%2C%20mixings%2C%20and%20cheese%20for%20Ina%20Garten's%20summery%20pasta%20salad%20recipe.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685af080f748d8c055f446d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22938%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20chopped%20and%20prepped%20all%20the%20salad's%20mix-ins%20while%20boiling%20water%20for%20the%20pasta.%3Cp%3ELizzy%20Briskin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20is%20the%20case%20with%20every%20good%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-chef-recipe-for-pasta-salad-reviewed-photos-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epasta-salad%20recipe%3C%2Fa%3E%20(in%20my%20opinion%2C%20anyway)%2C%20it's%20not%20overly%20complicated%20or%20time-intensive%20to%20prep%20the%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20boiled%20a%20big%20pot%20of%20salted%20water%20for%20the%20pasta%2C%20I%20chopped%20the%20fresh%20tomatoes%2C%20sliced%20the%20olives%2C%20and%20diced%20the%20feta%20and%20sun-dried%20tomatoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarten%20calls%20for%20diced%20whole%20tomatoes%2C%20but%20I%20used%20cherry%20tomatoes%20and%20simply%20sli