e%20used%20to%20be%20a%20sight%20to%20behold.%20No%20one%20was%20spared%2C%20not%20the%20nurses%20%E2%80%94%20Arjun%20would%20say%20to%20them%3A%20%E2%80%98May%20your%20efforts%20go%20in%20vain%20(a%20pun%20on%20vein%2C%20see%3F)%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20and%20quiz%20the%20anesthesiologist%2C%20%E2%80%98On%20dates%2C%20do%20you%20tell%20the%20other%20person%20you%20knock%20people%20out%3F%E2%80%99%20The%20medics%20would%20laugh.%20He%20would%20laugh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20surgery%20would%20commence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20his%20candour%2C%20Arjun%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20shy%20away%20from%20vulnerability.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20night%20before%20every%20surgery%2C%20reality%20would%20hit%3B%20I%E2%80%99d%20realise%20that%20the%20failure%20or%20success%20of%20the%20surgery%20would%20dictate%20whether%20I%20would%20live%20or%20not.%20As%20human%20beings%2C%20we%20have%20limitations%20and%20breaking%20points.%20There%20are%20times%20when%20one%20thing%20would%20happen%20after%20another%2C%20and%20I%20would%20feel%20like%20giving%20up%20hope.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20he%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20my%20core%20was%20the%20belief%20that%20someday%20death%20will%20win%2C%20but%20until%20then%2C%20my%20mind%20must.%E2%80%9D%20The%20secret%20lay%20in%20trading%20his%20vocabulary%20of%20fear%20for%20one%20of%20hope.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20today%2C%20look%20at%20him!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%E2%80%99ve%20been%20close%20to%20him%20would%20agree%20that%20his%20journey%20would%20pale%20any%20movie%20in%20comparison.%20Director%20Shoojit%20Sircar%20of%20%3Cem%3EPiku%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2015)%20and%20%3Cem%3EVicky%20Donor%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2012)%20fame%20seemed%20to%20think%20so%20too.%20His%20slice-of-life%20film%20%3Cem%3EI%20Want%20to%20Talk%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20an%20emotionally%20beguiling%20story%20of%20the%20complexities%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F45