%20with%20care%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20planting%20saplings%2C%20gently%20tease%20out%20roots%20that%20have%20become%20pot-bound%20to%20encourage%20outward%20growth.%20Place%20the%20sapling%20in%20the%20hole%20so%20that%20the%20root%20collar%20(where%20the%20roots%20meet%20the%20stem)%20is%20level%20with%20the%20surrounding%20soil%20surface.%20Backfill%20with%20the%20enriched%20soil%2C%20firming%20lightly%20but%20not%20compacting%20too%20much%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F417456%2Fhow-to-grow-raspuri-mangoes-karnataka-step-by-step-guide%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroots%20need%20air%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20seeds%2C%20plant%20them%20about%20two%20to%20three%20centimetres%20deep.%20Keep%20the%20soil%20consistently%20moist%20but%20not%20soggy%2C%20too%20much%20water%20can%20cause%20seeds%20to%20rot.%20Cover%20loosely%20with%20soil%20and%20water%20gently.%20Germination%20typically%20takes%20three%20to%20four%20weeks%2C%20sometimes%20longer%2C%20so%20patience%20is%20the%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMulching%20the%20planted%20area%20immediately%20with%20organic%20material%20like%20dried%20leaves%20or%20straw%20helps%20retain%20moisture%20and%20regulate%20temperature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Water%20regularly%2C%20but%20avoid%20waterlogging%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWatering%20chikoo%20during%20the%20monsoon%20requires%20a%20gentle%20hand.%20Although%20the%20rains%20provide%20plenty%20of%20moisture%2C%20monitor%20the%20soil%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20does%20not%20become%20waterlogged%2C%20as%20this%20can%20suffocate%20roots%20and%20lead%20to%20fungal%20diseases%20like%20root%20rot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Moder