e-460296%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGautam%20Raikar%2C%20a%2043-year-old%20engineer%20left%20behind%20a%20career%20in%20electronics%20distribution%20to%20start%20Liki%20Foods%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20journey%20began%20in%202018%20with%20a%20small%20outlet%20selling%20millet%20breads%2C%20rusks%2C%20and%20cookies.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20has%20grown%20it%20into%20a%20profitable%20store%20focused%20on%20dairy-free%20and%20nutrient-packed%20ice%20cream%20that%20is%20making%20waves%20across%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20Shivamogga%20and%20educated%20both%20there%20and%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20he%20was%20always%20inclined%20towards%20entrepreneurship%20rather%20than%20following%20the%20tech%20industry%20path%20his%20engineering%20degree%20might%20have%20suggested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20part%20of%20my%20family%E2%80%99s%20electronics%20distribution%20business%2C%20but%20I%20never%20really%20wanted%20to%20work%20in%20that%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20discovered%20that%20millet%20ice%20cream%20was%20almost%20non-existent%20in%20the%20market%2C%20I%20knew%20this%20was%20an%20opportunity%20to%20offer%20something%20different%20and%20unique%20to%20all%20dessert%20lovers%20looking%20for%20a%20healthier%20alternative.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20ice%20cream%3F%20The%20ingenious%20way%20to%20win%20over%20young%20taste%20buds%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMillets%20are%20known%20for%20being%20rich%20in%20iron%2C%20calcium%2C%20potassium%2C%20and%20other%20essential%20minerals.%20Yet%2C%20the%20entrepreneur%20noticed%20a%20common%20problem.%20%E2%80%9CChildren%20generally%20dislike%20the%20taste%20of%20millets%2C%20which%20limits%20their%20consumption.%20I%20believed%20ice%20cream%20could%20be%20a%20clever%20way%20to%20overcome%20that%20barrier.%20It%20is%20familiar%2C%20enjoyable%2