opics%2C%20ensuring%20that%20complex%20information%20can%20be%20quickly%20recalled.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20where%20I%20was%20lagging%20in%20Geography%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20I%20made%20the%20mistake%20of%20not%20making%20concise%20notes%2C%20and%20at%20the%20end%2C%20I%20had%20massive%20and%20cluttered%20notes%2C%20which%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20revise%20the%20concepts.%20This%20time%2C%20I%20learnt%20my%20lesson%20and%20prepared%20clear%20notes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4)%20Practice%20with%20previous%20year%20questions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20consistently%20practiced%20the%20previous%2010%20years%E2%80%99%20question%20papers%20multiple%20times%20to%20sharpen%20his%20answer-writing%20skills%20and%20get%20himself%20accustomed%20to%20the%20exam%20pattern.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20practice%20not%20only%20familiarised%20me%20with%20the%20exam%20pattern%20but%20also%20honed%20my%20real-time%20answer%20writing%20abilities%2C%20which%20is%20crucial%20for%20performing%20well%20in%20the%20mains%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5)%20Value%20addition%20through%20case%20studies%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollecting%20case%20studies%20and%20integrating%20them%20into%20his%20answers%20was%20a%20strategy%20Ajay%20used%20to%20add%20depth%20and%20differentiate%20his%20answers%20in%20optional%20papers%20from%20General%20Studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20a%20conscious%20effort%20to%20understand%20where%20and%20how%20to%20apply%20anthropological%20theories%20in%20different%20contexts.%20This%20involved%20thinking%20about%20possible%20scenarios%20and%20jotting%20down%20topics%20where%20these%20theories%20could%20be%20relevant.%20This%2C%20he%20says%2C%20enhanced%20the%20quality%20of%20his%20answers.%20%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20checking%20notes%20from%20previous%20toppers%20helped%20in%20deriving%20innovative%20ideas%20for%20value%20addition%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6)%20Rigorous%20answer%20writing%20practice%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevoting%20two%20hours%20daily%20to%20practice%20answer%20writing%20was%20a%20non-negotiable%20part%20of%20Ajay%E2%80%99s%20preparation.%20He%20focussed%20on%20writing%208-10%20answers%20each%20day%20across%20various%20question%20types%20(10%2C%2015%2C%20and%2020%20marker%20questions).%20Weekly%20tests%20were%20a%20staple%20in%20his%20routine%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20simulate%20exam%20conditions%20and%20manage%20his%20time%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7)%20Enhance%20presentation%20skills%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20also%20used%20diagrams%2C%20such%20as%20human%20skeletal%20structures%2C%20to%20enhance%20his%20answers%20in%20questions%20related%20to%20anthropological%20studies.%20These%20creative%20presentations%20added%20an%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20Ajay%20successfully%20cleared%20the%20prestigious%20UPSC%20CSE%2C%20securing%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%20705.%20Now%20an%20Indian%20Revenue%20Service%20officer%2C%20he%20eagerly%20awaits%20his%20journey%20to%20the%20Lal%20Bahadur%20Shastri%20National%20Academy%20of%20Administration%20(LBSNAA)%20in%20Mussoorie%20for%20his%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20courtesy%20Ajay%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751466600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FAjay-IRS-upsc-cse-3-1751458710.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D460341%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20peers%20advising%20against%20it%2C%20Haryana-based%20Ajay%20switched%20his%20UPSC%20optional%20due%20to%20persistent%20low%20scores.%20Anthropology%20offered%20a%20concise%2C%20defined%20syllabus%2C%20predictability%2C%20personal%20interest%2C%20and%20a%20multidisciplinary%20appeal.%20The%20IRS%20officer%20shares%20seven%20ultimate%20tips%20for%20a