20the%20corporate%20ladder%20is%20often%20seen%20as%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20success%2C%20Kotinaga%20Manikanta%20and%20Naga%20Venkata%20Durga%20Pavani%20took%20a%20bold%20and%20unconventional%20leap.%20Both%20BTech%20graduates%20initially%20followed%20the%20well-trodden%20path%20of%20the%20IT%20industry%20after%20completing%20their%20degrees.%20However%2C%20leaving%20behind%20the%20stability%20and%20rewards%20of%20their%20successful%20careers%2C%20this%20husband-and-wife%20duo%20from%20Guntur%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20traded%20boardrooms%20for%20farm%20fields%2C%20all%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F261242%2Fterrace-gardening-tips-youtube-organic-food-diet-thyroid%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epursuit%20of%20healthier%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20better%20world%20for%20farmers%20and%20consumers%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManikanta%20worked%20at%20Infosys%2C%20and%20Pavani%20at%20Accenture%2C%20both%20carving%20out%20solid%20careers%20in%20the%20fast-paced%2C%20technology-driven%20world.%20But%20despite%20significant%20success%2C%20they%20felt%20something%20was%20missing.%20%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20many%20colleagues%20in%20the%20IT%20sector%20struggling%20with%20health%20issues%2C%20despite%20their%20well-paying%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manikanta%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20leading%20sedentary%20lifestyles%2C%20and%20it%20made%20us%20realise%20that%20there%20was%20an%20opportunity%20to%20make%20a%20real%20difference%20in%20their%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Pavani.%20This%20realisation%2C%20combined%20with%20a%20desire%20to%20contribute%20more%20meaningfully%20to%20society%2C%20planted%20the%20seeds%20for%20%E2%80%98Sreshte%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20store%20for%20all%20organic%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20observed%20the%20growing%20health%20issues%20tied%20to%20poor%20diets%20and%20inactive%20lifestyles%2C%20they%20also%20became%20increasingly%20aware%20of%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20organic%20farmers%20in%20securing%20reliable%20markets%20for%20their%20produce.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20profit%2C%20but%20about%20making%20a%20genuine%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pavani%20reflects.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20believed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356941%2Forganic-farming-mba-grad-earns-crores-earthy-tales-delhi-ncr-deepak-sabharwal-rajasthan-farm-pesticides%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20be%20the%20solution%2C%20not%20only%20for%20the%20health%20of%20consumers%20but%20also%20for%20the%20farmers%20committed%20to%20sustainable%20practices.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20IT%20offices%20to%20farm%20fields%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20prior%20experience%20in%20farming%2C%20Manikanta%20and%20Pavani%20embarked%20on%20an%20intense%20learning%20journey.%20They%20enrolled%20in%20the%20Subash%20Palekar%20Natural%20Farming%20(SPNF)%20method%2C%20a%20technique%20that%20focuses%20on%20sustainability%20and%20eliminates%20the%20use%20of%20chemicals%20and%20pesticides.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20attending%20training%20sessions%20on%20weekends%20in%20our%20village%2C%20Lachannagudipudi%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20while%20working%20in%20Chennai%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manikanta.%20%E2%80%9CBalancing%20our%20full-time%20IT%20jobs%20and%20weekend%20training%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy%2C%20but%20our%20passion%20for%20making%20a%20change%20kept%20us%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20after%20months%20of%20rigorous%20learning%20and%20careful%20planning%2C%20the%20couple%20made%20a%20life-changing%20decision.%20They%20left%20their%20stable%20IT%20careers%20behind%20and%20returned%20to%20Guntur%2C%20investing%20their%20savings%20of%20Rs%2017%20lakh%20into%20a%20new%20